\end_inset

, and compare them.
 Central space is 
\begin_inset Formula $D^{-m}\tilde{H}^{s}/P_{m-1}$
\end_inset

 with Hilbert structure.
 Its dual contains 
\begin_inset Formula $H_{comp}^{-m-s}\cap P_{m-1}^{o}$
\end_inset

 as a dense subset (
